actions.recommendation: You are carrying a lot of excess weight and your body is taking strain. Sustainably loosing weight (diet/ exercise) will greatly benefit not only your joints, general mood, hormone levels but also your chronic conditions. Preventing complications and future cardiovascular events.

There is a family history of Prostate Cancer (father). Regular screening can help early detection & management of any abnormalities (greatly improves outcomes). Your PSA level (blood marker) was normal. I would recommend a regular clinical prostate examination & repeated blood levels.
